						               													<description>This game (which could be translated to &amp;quot;Superhero Academy&amp;quot;) is about Polish scientist that made a great impact in the history of science.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game consist of 30 cards with a different scientist on each card. On a player's turn they draw a card from the pile and ask other players questions (which are actually clues) about the scientist (the questions are presented on the cards). The first player to guess which scientist the question(s) refer(s) to score 1-3 points depending on how many clue-questions they needed (more clues - less points).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game ends when there are no cards in the pile and the player who scored the most points is the winner.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;user summary&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Akademia Superbohater&amp;oacute;w to fascynuj&amp;#196;&amp;#133;ca rozgyrwka, kt&amp;oacute;ra pozwala odkry&amp;#196;&amp;#135; znanych i nieznanych polskich bohater&amp;oacute;w.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Gra karciana w formie quizu. Przeznaczona jest dla minimum dw&amp;oacute;ch graczy w wieku od 7 lat (gracze musz&amp;#196;&amp;#133; umie&amp;#196;&amp;#135; czyta&amp;#196;&amp;#135;). Jej celem jest zgromadzenie jak najwi&amp;#196;&amp;#153;kszej liczby punkt&amp;oacute;w.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Punkty s&amp;#196;&amp;#133; przyznawane za wiedz&amp;#196;&amp;#153; o najwi&amp;#196;&amp;#153;kszych polskich naukowacach, a tak&amp;#197;&amp;#188;e za refleks.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the back of the box&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
